{"tid":249291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【UGL醜聞】民主派斥事態嚴重 擬6月彈劾梁振英","createTime":"2017-05-19T07:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T18:18:52.000Z","uid":91283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46be68be7a167df118f77e910640b7c84ed81e0d","tid":249291,"uid":91283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"特首梁振英被揭與民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎打龍通，利用周向立會調查UGL專責委員會提出其個人意見，民主派議員今日舉行特別會議商議事件，擬於下月根據《基本法》啟動彈劾梁振英議案。<br />\n<br />\n泛民會議召集人涂謹申指，雖然梁振英任期只餘下一個多月，但由於事態嚴重，認為應讓議員在大會上就事件辯論及討論。他透露民主派初步已草擬議案措辭，最快在6月7日大會上提出，否則需延至6月14日提出。<br />\n公民黨郭榮鏗直言在建制派護航的情況下，相信難以取得足夠票數，但認為有需要在立法會留下一個紀錄，證明梁振英曾做過「咁離譜嘅事」。<br />\n對於周浩鼎今早去信調查UGL事件專委會主席，即時辭去專委會委員職務，涂謹申指民主派仍會繼續在下月7日大會提出譴責議案，要求取消其議員資格。  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170519/56714816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170519%2F56714816&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=246c7a8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170519%2F56714816&h=0bc883f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170519/56714816</a>"},{"pid":"937e5e29c80772a6c7859305d6761b1d40ecb3db","tid":249291,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c082d65997c3f987c5db8ef21a874ca2eace4a35","tid":249291,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"80124c17e513c8cf948ad25942a1a04d7c85bbb4","tid":249291,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"成班飯桶<br />\n到時有功就出黎邀"},{"pid":"fca2a48bf44ffd6c74708dd885c579c33fd279fa","tid":249291,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}